v></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1848_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-1849_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-1850_">Bridging the accessibility gap</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/paradise-will-be-a-kind-of-a-library-shot-of-a-yo-2023-11-27-04-56-04-utc.jpg?v=1709641147" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/paradise-will-be-a-kind-of-a-library-shot-of-a-yo-2023-11-27-04-56-04-utc.jpg?v=1709641147 1536w" width="1000" height="667" alt="Unlock the Power of Learning: Top Educational Resources for World Book Day - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Unlock the Power of Learning: Top Educational Resources for World Book Day - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-1852_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-1853_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by YuriArcursPeopleimages via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-1855_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Organisations like Book Aid International and the World Literacy Foundation play pivotal roles in ensuring that books reach the hands of those in underprivileged communities. These organisations work relentlessly to bridge the gap, making literature accessible to all and fostering a global reading culture.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1857_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-1858_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-1859_">Celebrating diversity through books</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/ge